WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:02.869
Hey, good morning, family. Praise the

00:00:02.879 --> 00:00:04.870
Lord. Well, I have my sweetheart with me

00:00:04.880 --> 00:00:06.869
today. She's behind the camera. She

00:00:06.879 --> 00:00:09.270
helps me pray when I pray. I said I miss

00:00:09.280 --> 00:00:11.430
her when she's not in here because I can

00:00:11.440 --> 00:00:13.589
feel her. We tug along together after

00:00:13.599 --> 00:00:15.270
being married for as long as we have.

00:00:15.280 --> 00:00:17.990
I just know, and it's a

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:20.470
blessing when she's here. You know,

00:00:20.480 --> 00:00:23.269
yesterday was a heavy word. There were a

00:00:23.279 --> 00:00:24.870
lot of things when we were driving

00:00:24.880 --> 00:00:26.950
around, and the Lord was showing me so

00:00:26.960 --> 00:00:30.630
much that seemed to be a

00:00:30.640 --> 00:00:33.750
real Debbie Downer. I mean, after it

00:00:33.760 --> 00:00:35.750
was over, I said, "Lord, that was

00:00:35.750 --> 00:00:35.760
heavy."And

00:00:35.760 --> 00:00:38.229
I was carrying it. I

00:00:38.239 --> 00:00:40.310
told Braden

00:00:40.320 --> 00:00:42.549
when he was editing the

00:00:42.559 --> 00:00:44.630
video, I said, "My goodness, I hope I

00:00:44.640 --> 00:00:46.470
didn't come across cranky."And he goes,

00:00:46.480 --> 00:00:49.350
"A little bit."And I said, "Well, when

00:00:49.360 --> 00:00:52.310
I'm carrying something so heavy, I might

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:54.310
come across kind of cranky, and I don't

00:00:54.320 --> 00:00:56.150
mean to, ladies and gentlemen. I want

00:00:56.160 --> 00:00:58.630
you to understand, I'm passionate about

00:00:58.640 --> 00:01:01.430
what the Lord shows me. I'm passionate

00:01:01.440 --> 00:01:03.590
about it. I believe in it, and I know

00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:05.270
what the Lord is trying to warn His

00:01:05.280 --> 00:01:08.390
people about. I have such an

00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:10.630
urgency, and that urgency and the

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:13.350
heaviness of what I have

00:01:13.350 --> 00:01:13.360
seen—because

00:01:13.360 --> 00:01:15.190
when you're seeing it, I describe it to

00:01:15.200 --> 00:01:17.510
you, but I've seen it literally, people

00:01:17.520 --> 00:01:19.590
falling down dead, things

00:01:19.590 --> 00:01:19.600
happening—it

00:01:19.600 --> 00:01:21.270
grieves you.

00:01:21.280 --> 00:01:23.830
It's heavy. And so I think

00:01:23.840 --> 00:01:26.870
sometimes the urgency of

00:01:26.880 --> 00:01:28.630
what I feel in my spirit comes across

00:01:28.640 --> 00:01:31.670
as cranky, and I apologize if it did,

00:01:31.680 --> 00:01:35.270
but I want you to understand it

00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:39.350
is very urgent. And I'm

00:01:39.360 --> 00:01:41.350
trying to get across that you need

00:01:41.360 --> 00:01:45.429
to listen. You know,

00:01:45.439 --> 00:01:48.550
I called my elders like

00:01:48.560 --> 00:01:50.630
Sister Billye yesterday, and I

00:01:50.640 --> 00:01:52.149
told her, "This is what I'm

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:53.510
seeing, and this is what the Lord's

00:01:53.520 --> 00:01:55.109
warning about, and I'm seeing these

00:01:55.119 --> 00:01:57.030
ministers die on the platform, and I want

00:01:57.040 --> 00:02:00.230
you to judge the words as an elder. I

00:02:00.240 --> 00:02:01.749
want you to listen to what I'm going to

00:02:01.759 --> 00:02:03.910
say. And if it doesn't line up in

00:02:03.920 --> 00:02:05.670
your spirit, if you feel that it's off

00:02:05.670 --> 00:02:05.680
too..."Because

00:02:05.680 --> 00:02:07.510
I don't want to be somebody

00:02:07.520 --> 00:02:09.350
leading people by the hundreds of

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:10.869
thousands, millions of people on a

00:02:10.879 --> 00:02:13.110
weekly basis, that comes across as

00:02:13.120 --> 00:02:15.510
flaky. But as an elder that's been in

00:02:15.520 --> 00:02:18.309
the faith

00:02:18.319 --> 00:02:20.390
preaching and teaching people about

00:02:20.400 --> 00:02:26.390
Jesus for 80-some years plus,

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:28.390
I just want you to listen to this

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:31.190
and let your spirit hear it. And

00:02:31.200 --> 00:02:32.630
she goes, "You know,

00:02:32.640 --> 00:02:34.630
Brandon, I'll judge the words, and I'll

00:02:34.640 --> 00:02:37.270
pray over them."And I appreciate

00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:39.270
somebody who has been in the Word for

00:02:39.280 --> 00:02:43.190
so long. I mean, she's my elder. And

00:02:43.200 --> 00:02:45.350
she prayed with me, she prayed for me,

00:02:45.360 --> 00:02:47.190
and just really uplifted me. We had a

00:02:47.200 --> 00:02:48.470
great conversation. And I want to tell

00:02:48.480 --> 00:02:50.470
you all, it's a real blessing to

00:02:50.480 --> 00:02:52.710
have somebody like that. I never take

00:02:52.720 --> 00:02:55.030
it for granted. It's a true blessing to

00:02:55.040 --> 00:02:57.190
be able to talk to somebody who is

00:02:57.200 --> 00:02:59.430
a

00:02:59.440 --> 00:03:01.430
seasoned minister that

00:03:01.440 --> 00:03:03.589
teaches about end times, teaches about

00:03:03.599 --> 00:03:06.229
prayer, teaches about eschatology, all

00:03:06.239 --> 00:03:08.869
the great stuff, and is accurate

00:03:08.879 --> 00:03:10.869
about things. And I give God

00:03:10.879 --> 00:03:12.470
praise for that opportunity to be able

00:03:12.480 --> 00:03:14.790
to talk to somebody that's not flaky,

00:03:14.800 --> 00:03:16.390
you know, that was around Brother

00:03:16.390 --> 00:03:16.400
Hagin,

00:03:16.400 --> 00:03:20.470
that was around John G.

00:03:20.470 --> 00:03:20.480
Lake's

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:22.550
daughter and all the greats. I

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:25.910
mean, seriously, it's amazing. So that

00:03:25.920 --> 00:03:27.830
being said, this is her

00:03:27.840 --> 00:03:30.710
praying over it and telling me

00:03:30.720 --> 00:03:32.309
basically she feels I'm on the right

00:03:32.319 --> 00:03:35.190
road. And she asked me,

00:03:35.200 --> 00:03:37.589
"What do you

00:03:37.599 --> 00:03:40.550
feel about the mega preacher

00:03:40.560 --> 00:03:44.070
that you saw being shot on the stage? There

00:03:44.070 --> 00:03:44.080
were

00:03:44.080 --> 00:03:46.390
two preachers, and

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:49.270
they were trying to bring fear

00:03:49.280 --> 00:03:51.270
for people not wanting to go into

00:03:51.270 --> 00:03:51.280
the revival."And

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:53.670
instantaneously, I

00:03:53.680 --> 00:03:56.550
said the Lord said, "Pray for this man

00:03:56.560 --> 00:03:59.670
that it does not take place."Now, the

00:03:59.680 --> 00:04:02.390
exposing of the church in California, we

00:04:02.400 --> 00:04:04.710
pray for the church in California. But

00:04:04.710 --> 00:04:04.720
the

00:04:04.720 --> 00:04:07.030
bottom line is that God told me,

00:04:07.040 --> 00:04:09.509
"Brandon, judgment begins in the house of

00:04:09.519 --> 00:04:11.990
the Lord first. And I'm cleaning up My

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:14.550
church right now. And many ministers

00:04:14.560 --> 00:04:16.870
that you see behind pulpits in the days

00:04:16.880 --> 00:04:20.150
ahead will not be there.

00:04:20.160 --> 00:04:23.510
I'm raising up new Davids, new voices

00:04:23.520 --> 00:04:26.150
with different influence in these end

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:29.590
times because the time is

00:04:29.590 --> 00:04:29.600
short."He

00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:31.670
said, "I'm going to pour out... this is

00:04:31.680 --> 00:04:34.070
a different mantle that we've never seen

00:04:34.070 --> 00:04:34.080
before."Like

00:04:34.080 --> 00:04:36.469
we've seen the John G.

00:04:36.479 --> 00:04:38.390
Lakes, the

00:04:38.390 --> 00:04:38.400
Oral

00:04:38.400 --> 00:04:40.629
Roberts, and the Jack Coe's. But the

00:04:40.639 --> 00:04:42.870
Lord showed me, He said, "Brandon, we're

00:04:42.880 --> 00:04:45.909
going to see a new era of creative

00:04:45.919 --> 00:04:47.909
miracles that the world has never seen

00:04:47.919 --> 00:04:50.710
before."Remember

00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:53.030
what I told you? I saw the chariots of

00:04:53.040 --> 00:04:55.749
fire all lined up in heaven, and they

00:04:55.759 --> 00:04:58.550
were all waiting for this

00:04:58.560 --> 00:05:00.950
great tidal wave that was coming on the

00:05:00.960 --> 00:05:04.950
earth. A massive tsunami wave of the

00:05:04.960 --> 00:05:08.150
glory of the Lord was coming on the

00:05:08.160 --> 00:05:10.790
earth. And I saw chariots of fire with

00:05:10.800 --> 00:05:13.270
packages all on the back of those

00:05:13.280 --> 00:05:16.150
chariots of fire. And the Lord told me,

00:05:16.160 --> 00:05:18.550
He said, "During the Christmas time,

00:05:18.560 --> 00:05:21.350
I'm delivering those giftings

00:05:21.360 --> 00:05:24.070
into 2025

00:05:24.080 --> 00:05:28.629
on the people who would receive

00:05:28.629 --> 00:05:28.639
them."Those

00:05:28.639 --> 00:05:31.189
chariots of fire were all

00:05:31.199 --> 00:05:33.029
around, and I could see them, and the

00:05:33.039 --> 00:05:35.270
packages were being delivered, and those

00:05:35.280 --> 00:05:38.790
are end-time giftings, and mantles were

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:42.310
being delivered to the people.

00:05:42.320 --> 00:05:45.110
It was a vision. But some of the gifts

00:05:45.120 --> 00:05:47.110
were not able to be delivered because

00:05:47.120 --> 00:05:49.830
the people weren't ready for them, and

00:05:49.840 --> 00:05:53.510
the chariot of fire went back up.

00:05:53.520 --> 00:05:55.029
That was a sad time. I was

00:05:55.039 --> 00:05:57.590
thinking, "Oh goodness, but I

00:05:57.600 --> 00:06:00.710
wanted just to receive mine."Do you

00:06:00.720 --> 00:06:02.870
understand? And there

00:06:02.870 --> 00:06:02.880
were

00:06:02.880 --> 00:06:04.790
literally thousands of chariots, and

00:06:04.800 --> 00:06:06.070
they were all bringing the

00:06:06.080 --> 00:06:07.189
giftings. And the Lord told me, He said,

00:06:07.199 --> 00:06:09.110
"This is for the end times,

00:06:09.110 --> 00:06:09.120
Brandon."So

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:11.670
those giftings are there, and that's

00:06:11.680 --> 00:06:13.909
what we're about to see:

00:06:13.919 --> 00:06:16.150
things and creative miracles that we've

00:06:16.160 --> 00:06:19.029
never seen before.

00:06:19.039 --> 00:06:22.469
What happened in the

00:06:22.479 --> 00:06:24.550
tent revival of old and the

00:06:24.560 --> 00:06:26.550
great things Oral Roberts and all of them

00:06:26.560 --> 00:06:29.670
did, that's the old things. And the Lord

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:32.550
said, "They barely touched a glass full

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:34.469
of what I'm wanting to do in this end-time

00:06:34.469 --> 00:06:34.479
move."And

00:06:34.479 --> 00:06:38.070
I saw a great well in

00:06:38.080 --> 00:06:40.629
Oral Roberts University. I saw a massive

00:06:40.639 --> 00:06:42.150
well,

00:06:42.160 --> 00:06:44.390
and everybody like Kenneth Hagin and

00:06:44.400 --> 00:06:46.629
these men of God were taking a cup and

00:06:46.639 --> 00:06:48.550
they were drinking out of that well. And

00:06:48.560 --> 00:06:50.950
He said, "This next generation, this

00:06:50.960 --> 00:06:54.150
last generation, this last push will go,

00:06:54.160 --> 00:06:56.150
and they'll dip their whole body in it.

00:06:56.160 --> 00:06:57.590
They're not just going to get a cup,

00:06:57.600 --> 00:06:59.430
Brandon. I'm going to take them to the

00:06:59.440 --> 00:07:01.990
deep parts of that well.

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:04.469
For what's about to take place has never

00:07:04.479 --> 00:07:07.830
been seen

00:07:07.830 --> 00:07:07.840
before."We're

00:07:07.840 --> 00:07:09.749
all excited about the glory

00:07:09.759 --> 00:07:11.510
cloud, and we get excited about what we

00:07:11.520 --> 00:07:13.270
heard happened at

00:07:13.270 --> 00:07:13.280
Azusa

00:07:13.280 --> 00:07:15.029
Street. But the Lord said to me, "That's

00:07:15.039 --> 00:07:16.950
old things, Brandon. Behold, I'm

00:07:16.960 --> 00:07:19.110
going to do something new, something

00:07:19.120 --> 00:07:23.430
that you've never seen

00:07:23.430 --> 00:07:23.440
before."He's

00:07:23.440 --> 00:07:26.070
multifaceted, ladies and gentlemen.

00:07:26.080 --> 00:07:28.950
We have not seen all the

00:07:28.960 --> 00:07:31.830
splendor of what God has for us. We've

00:07:31.840 --> 00:07:34.150
only seen little glimpses of what He's

00:07:34.160 --> 00:07:37.749
allowed for that season.

00:07:37.759 --> 00:07:40.390
"Think bigger,"is what the Lord told me to

00:07:40.400 --> 00:07:43.430
tell you all today. Think bigger. You

00:07:43.440 --> 00:07:46.870
need to believe for bigger. What is

00:07:46.880 --> 00:07:49.589
it to you

00:07:49.599 --> 00:07:52.469
when I told you the scripture that when

00:07:52.479 --> 00:07:55.749
Moses had so much overflow, and I had my

00:07:55.759 --> 00:07:58.629
wife read it, about so much overflow

00:07:58.639 --> 00:08:01.830
that Moses said there's not enough room

00:08:01.840 --> 00:08:04.469
in the storehouse to take any more

00:08:04.479 --> 00:08:06.629
blessing?

00:08:06.639 --> 00:08:09.270
There's too much. We can't receive it

00:08:09.280 --> 00:08:11.909
all. And the Lord said, "Brandon, it's a

00:08:11.919 --> 00:08:13.990
type and shadow of what I'm going to do

00:08:14.000 --> 00:08:16.070
for you in these last days for My

00:08:16.080 --> 00:08:18.230
remnant. That it'll be too much. There's

00:08:18.240 --> 00:08:20.869
not room enough to receive it

00:08:20.869 --> 00:08:20.879
all."But

00:08:20.879 --> 00:08:23.510
not only that, they left healed, and

00:08:23.520 --> 00:08:26.150
there wasn't a feeble one among them.

00:08:26.160 --> 00:08:28.869
And the Lord said, "Brandon, if I did it

00:08:28.879 --> 00:08:30.790
for the children of Israel leaving

00:08:30.800 --> 00:08:33.029
Egypt, I'll do it for My bride that's

00:08:33.039 --> 00:08:35.350
leaving this earth."Do you understand

00:08:35.360 --> 00:08:38.149
what I'm about to do in this earth? In

00:08:38.159 --> 00:08:41.269
this last generation, there will

00:08:41.279 --> 00:08:43.829
be no feeble among you. Do you

00:08:43.839 --> 00:08:45.350
understand? There's not going to be any

00:08:45.360 --> 00:08:48.150
sick people. You will have to resist

00:08:48.160 --> 00:08:50.790
healing:

00:08:50.800 --> 00:08:52.389
"I don't want to be healed,

00:08:52.389 --> 00:08:52.399
Lord."He

00:08:52.399 --> 00:08:53.990
said, "I'm going to pour it out

00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:56.550
upon all flesh, Brandon, if you just

00:08:56.560 --> 00:08:59.990
believe me for it.

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:02.470
With simple faith,

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:04.949
what seemed to be the impossible will

00:09:04.959 --> 00:09:07.269
become possible if you just believe him

00:09:07.279 --> 00:09:09.030
for it.

00:09:09.040 --> 00:09:11.190
So, I'm here to tell you today, yes,

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:13.190
there's a great shaking. But people say,

00:09:13.200 --> 00:09:15.269
'How can these things be, Brandon, if

00:09:15.279 --> 00:09:17.030
you're telling us all these dark things

00:09:17.040 --> 00:09:19.509
are coming and all this disruption and

00:09:19.519 --> 00:09:22.870
all the social unrest and all the sad

00:09:22.880 --> 00:09:24.949
days, the plague and all this

00:09:24.949 --> 00:09:24.959
stuff?'He

00:09:24.959 --> 00:09:27.030
said, 'Arise and shine, for the light

00:09:27.040 --> 00:09:29.350
has come and the glory of the Lord is

00:09:29.360 --> 00:09:30.949
risen on you, ladies and

00:09:30.949 --> 00:09:30.959
gentlemen.'And

00:09:30.959 --> 00:09:32.470
he said, 'Brandon, it will be like a

00:09:32.470 --> 00:09:32.480
quarter.'I've

00:09:32.480 --> 00:09:34.150
told you this so many

00:09:34.160 --> 00:09:35.990
times. He said, 'It will be like a

00:09:36.000 --> 00:09:38.550
quarter.

00:09:38.560 --> 00:09:41.030
It'll be that thin.

00:09:41.040 --> 00:09:43.670
You can either look on the dark, for the

00:09:43.680 --> 00:09:45.990
dark will get darker,

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:47.829
but the light is going to be on the

00:09:47.839 --> 00:09:49.750
other side, and the light will be

00:09:49.760 --> 00:09:51.990
lighter and lighter. It'll be so dark in

00:09:52.000 --> 00:09:54.790
the world, Brandon, just like it was in

00:09:54.800 --> 00:09:58.389
Egypt. It'll be so dark,

00:09:58.399 --> 00:10:01.110
it'll be tangible. Do you understand?

00:10:01.120 --> 00:10:02.710
That's what I'm trying to say. It'll be

00:10:02.720 --> 00:10:06.470
tangible darkness like it was in Egypt.

00:10:06.480 --> 00:10:10.550
But just across the street, there was

00:10:10.560 --> 00:10:13.990
glory and there was light on God's

00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:15.670
people.'The

00:10:15.680 --> 00:10:17.350
Lord said to me, he said, "Brandon,

00:10:17.360 --> 00:10:18.790
that's how much it's going to be like

00:10:18.790 --> 00:10:18.800
now—a

00:10:18.800 --> 00:10:22.949
type and shadow again of great

00:10:22.959 --> 00:10:25.190
darkness on the earth, and it will be

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:27.509
tangible. You're going to turn on

00:10:27.519 --> 00:10:30.069
the news and you're going to go, 'Oh

00:10:30.079 --> 00:10:32.790
my gosh, the sky is falling, Chicken

00:10:32.790 --> 00:10:32.800
Little!'Or

00:10:32.800 --> 00:10:34.870
you can look at what's going

00:10:34.880 --> 00:10:36.470
on in the church and say, 'Whoa, the

00:10:36.480 --> 00:10:39.509
glory's happening, Jesus!'Do you

00:10:39.519 --> 00:10:41.030
understand?

00:10:41.040 --> 00:10:43.990
It will be that thin of a line. You can

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:47.030
either go vertical or you can go

00:10:47.030 --> 00:10:47.040
horizontal."And

00:10:47.040 --> 00:10:48.790
I said, "If you keep

00:10:48.800 --> 00:10:50.870
your eyes on what's going on in the news

00:10:50.880 --> 00:10:52.790
every day for what's coming, ladies and

00:10:52.800 --> 00:10:55.590
gentlemen, men's hearts will fail them

00:10:55.600 --> 00:10:57.750
for fear, looking after those things

00:10:57.760 --> 00:11:00.230
that are coming on the

00:11:00.230 --> 00:11:00.240
earth."And

00:11:00.240 --> 00:11:01.269
people are going to be freaked out with

00:11:01.279 --> 00:11:03.509
the volcanoes, the earthquakes, the war,

00:11:03.519 --> 00:11:06.949
the rumors of war. Or you can focus

00:11:06.959 --> 00:11:09.269
on the brush arbor churches, you

00:11:09.279 --> 00:11:11.670
can focus on the limbs growing out and

00:11:11.680 --> 00:11:13.350
people getting delivered and healed and

00:11:13.360 --> 00:11:15.509
